1. *Mora* da se spremi za ispite. (She must prepare for the exams.)
2. On *mora* da radi u nedelju. (He has to work on Sunday.)
3. Ona *mora* da ima 18 godina. (She must be 18 years old.)
4. Oni *moraju* da se pridržavaju pravila. (They must abide by the rules.)
5. Ona *mora* da ide rano na posao. (She has to go to work early.)
6. Njihov pas *mora* da bude vakcinisan. (Their dog has to be vaccinated.)
7. *Mora* da se zahvali za poklon. (She must thank for the present.)
8. Oni *moraju* da kontrolišu svoje troškove. (They have to control their expenses.)